# consciousness-server CODEOWNERS
#
# GitHub reads this file and requires the listed reviewer(s) to
# approve any PR that touches the matching paths. The point is not
# "one maintainer bottlenecks all work" — the point is that
# relaxing a security invariant or changing the architectural
# contract never happens silently.
#
# Whoever is the acting maintainer at the time the repo is deployed
# commercially should replace @tmaloziec with their handle + any
# co-owners. Before then this file documents intent.

# Default — any change needs a maintainer look.
*                                       @tmaloziec

# Core block (the consciousness-server itself).
/core/                                  @tmaloziec

# Shared middleware masters. A change here is a change to the
# signed-request semantics of EVERY block via bin/sync-middleware.
/lib/                                   @tmaloziec

# Per-block middleware copies. Normally regenerated by sync-middleware,
# but a direct edit would let a rogue PR silently weaken one block's gate.
/core/middleware/                       @tmaloziec
/semantic-search/middleware/            @tmaloziec
/machines-server/middleware/            @tmaloziec
/test-runner/middleware/                @tmaloziec
/git-workflow/middleware/               @tmaloziec
/key-server/middleware/                 @tmaloziec

# Auth surface. Any change to the signing protocol, the verify
# endpoint, or the IP/allowlist logic needs review.
/key-server/                            @tmaloziec
/docs/SIGNING-PROTOCOL.md               @tmaloziec
/docs/AUTH-MODE.md                      @tmaloziec

# Protect CI config + this file itself — otherwise a PR could
# disable the guards or drop the ownership rule in the same diff.
/.github/                               @tmaloziec
/CODEOWNERS                             @tmaloziec

# Deployment surface — touching compose, volumes, or env defaults
# can change the blast radius of a running ecosystem.
/deploy/                                @tmaloziec

# Architectural contract. ARCHITECTURE.md is the source of truth;
# code drift is resolved in favour of this file.
/ARCHITECTURE.md                        @tmaloziec

# Operator scripts — they run with the operator's privileges.
/bin/                                   @tmaloziec

# Commercial licensing surface — change intent, not just prose.
/LICENSE                                @tmaloziec
/LICENSE-COMMERCIAL.md                  @tmaloziec
/CLA.md                                 @tmaloziec
/CONTRIBUTING.md                        @tmaloziec
/COPYRIGHT                              @tmaloziec
/SECURITY.md                            @tmaloziec
